reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally have a paci that my baby will take!
reviews.reviewText: As a parent to a newborn, the quest for the perfect pacifier has been a journey of trial and error, but the Nanobebe Active Baby Pacifiers have truly been a game-changer in soothing my little one.What sets these pacifiers apart is the clever design that mirrors the shape of the Nanobebe bottles my baby already loves. This consistency in design has made transitioning from bottle to pacifier a seamless experience. My baby immediately recognized the familiar shape and has readily accepted the Nanobebe pacifier, making it the first and only pacifier she has taken.The silicone construction is a standout feature for me as a parent. Unlike traditional pacifiers made of plastic, the Nanobebe pacifiers are gentle on my baby's delicate face. The soft, flexible silicone conforms to her mouth without leaving any marks, ensuring comfort during extended use. It's reassuring to know that the material is safe and gentle, especially during those precious moments of soothing and comfort.The design of the pacifier is thoughtful and well-executed. The shield is contoured to provide good airflow, preventing any irritation or discomfort. The orthodontic shape supports healthy oral development, which is essential for my baby's growing mouth. The one-piece construction also means there are no small parts that could pose a choking hazard, providing peace of mind for this vigilant parent.The fact that the Nanobebe pacifier is the same as the bottles my baby uses is a major convenience. I can easily switch between the two without any confusion or resistance from my little one. It's a practical choice that streamlines our daily routine, making life a bit easier for both baby and parent.In conclusion, the Nanobebe Active Baby Pacifiers have exceeded my expectations as a parent. The familiar bottle-like design, gentle silicone construction, and thoughtful features make them a standout choice in the world of pacifiers. If you're looking for a pacifier that aligns with your baby's preferences, supports healthy oral development, and provides peace of mind, the Nanobebe pacifiers are a fantastic choice for soothing and comforting your little one.

reviews.reviewText: These pacifiers works great for my little guy! Introduced them at 10 days and didn’t have any nipple confusion. I also like that they are made completely of soft silicone and have no hard parts. Easy to clean and come in nice colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Our baby loves it!
reviews.reviewText: Simple design, and works better than any other pacifiers we’ve used. After 3 babies, it’s my favorite. We got the infant pacifier and the 6-36 month size. It’s the only one we’ve found that was small enough to fit his tiny mouth. We also love that it doubles as a chew toy for him teething since it’s all made of solid silicon. It’s also light weight so he doesn’t have to suck too hard to keep it in. No hard plastic, only soft silicon, and doesn’t have a huge circle to block breathing though tiny nostrils like his avent pacifier. It sends like it will be easier to ween from, as well. I highly recommend. Perfect for newborns and premies.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on May 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased a baby dummy for my little one, and I must say it has been a lifesaver! This dummy is not only adorable but also highly functional. It is made of soft, BPA-free silicone material that feels gentle against my baby's skin.One of the best features of this dummy is its orthodontic design, which helps promote healthy oral development. It fits comfortably in my baby's mouth and doesn't cause any discomfort. Plus, the shield is perfectly sized, preventing any choking hazards.Cleaning the dummy is a breeze too. It can be easily sterilized by boiling or using a sterilizer, ensuring maximum hygiene for my baby. The durability of the dummy is impressive as well. It has withstood countless drops and bites without showing any signs of wear and tear.Another great aspect is the availability of various cute designs and colors to choose from. It adds a fun and playful touch to my baby's overall look.Overall, I highly recommend this baby dummy. It provides comfort, safety, and style all in one. My baby loves it, and I couldn't be happier with my purchase.
